flowchart TD
    Content[Untrusted Content] --> Q[Quarantined LLM<br/>NO tools]
    Q --> Summary[Sanitized Summary]
    Summary --> Controller[Controller<br/>Deterministic Validation]
    Controller -->|passed| P[Privileged LLM<br/>Has tools]
    Controller -->|flagged| Block[Blocked]
    P --> Action[Tool Execution]
    
    style Q fill:#f08c00,color:#fff
    style Controller fill:#868e96,color:#fff
    style P fill:#1971c2,color:#fff
    style Block fill:#e03131,color:#fff
    style Action fill:#2f9e44,color:#fff
